title: Jenn-Air® Induction Downdraft Cooktop | Jenn-Air
description: The Jenn-Air® Induction Downdraft Cooktop blends our leadership in ventilation with powerful and efficient induction cooking elements. Keeping sight lines open while offering exceptional efficiency and flexibility, this cooktop offers the cooking power of gas and the cleanability of electric while rapidly clearing the air of cooking vapors without the need for an overhead ventilation system. And with smart features, like performance boost for quickly heating cookware to pan detection sensors that automatically turn an element on or off, cooking efficiently and safely has never been easier.
